09084226","tid":1776281,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8229424ae32ec3207d69959c25ad499df41c2c1","tid":1776281,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=f3f5de38\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"0f0bf31197557277b8f6f4366121c7fdf1e6bbc3","tid":1776281,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"又ot，721 831"},{"pid":"217e5e8f0c0c5e39200d65d03e0aac4e9a19825f","tid":1776281,"uid":332807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4742b0b777c740eb0072ad28bee8bafb09084226","tid":1776281,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"求link"},{"pid":"81d81b7a5f5404a9b53fa900daf930b8